WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.110 --> 00:00:07.030
Mrs. Blair? Mrs. Blair, you have a concussion.

2
00:00:07.030 --> 00:00:10.380
We need your next to kin to sign up on your discharge.

3
00:00:10.380 --> 00:00:14.380
Uh, I'll call my husband Nolan Blair. He's a firefighter.

4
00:00:14.380 --> 00:00:22.980
He's called Nolan. Leave a message.

5
00:00:22.980 --> 00:01:18.299
I need to talk to you.

6
00:01:18.299 --> 00:01:19.879
Not now.

7
00:01:19.879 --> 00:01:21.879
It's so important that you can't talk to your own wife.

8
00:01:21.879 --> 00:01:26.359
You're a contract wife, not a real one. Don't call me at work again.

